# HR ERP orchestrator

**Team map:** [agent-team-map.md](../../docs/meta/agent-team-map.md) · **Process:** [hooks.json](../hooks.json) · **Invariants:** [repo-boundaries.mdc](repo-boundaries.mdc) · **Skills:** `@skill-router` · `~/.cursor/skills/README.md`

Global core: `~/.cursor/rules/core-orchestrator.mdc` + `core-dynamic-skills.mdc` (advisory when `hookEnforcement: true`).

## Quick start

0. Collaboration phases 1–3: `@hr-human-collaboration` + [collaboration-plan.md](../../specs/templates/collaboration-plan.md)
1. Load [agent-team-map.md](../../docs/meta/agent-team-map.md) (team roster)
2. `npm run governance:lint` → tier + required lanes
3. `npm run governance:plan` → DAG JSON for handoff / hooks
4. `/multitask` · `/worktree` (DDL) · `/best-of-n` (T4 repair) per `@hr-orchestration-lanes`
5. T2+: `specs/**/orchestrator-handoff.json` with `delegatedTaskPlan` matching Required lanes
6. `npm run governance:ci` before merge (PRs)

**Hook rollout:** counsel-before-builder denies T3+ builder Tasks from `preToolUseDenyT3From` ([hook-mode.json](../governance/hook-mode.json)). Check: `npm run governance:hooks:status`.

Manifest v4: [governance-manifest.yaml](../governance/governance-manifest.yaml) · ADRs [0016–0020](../../specs/alignment/decisions/0016-agent-harness-foundation.md)

**Collaboration plane (ADR 0020):** seven-phase Harness HITL; specialized skills after `revalidationConfirmed`; timeout=deny.

**Phase 2 (ADR 0019):** evidence bundles (`governance:evidence`), cloud session ledger, strict VDR for T1+ — see `@hr-foundation-governance`.

Precedence: Human PO → PO checkpoint → counsel → Security merge bar.
